يلة أو الدويلات الطائفية العدمية بلا وحدة ولا نهضة ولا حرية.</span></p><p dir="rtl" style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;height:11pt;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-weight:bold"></span></p><p dir="rtl" style="font-size:11pt;padding:0;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin:0;color:#000000;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#990000;font-weight:bold">* </span><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-weight:bold">الكاتب الأمريكي تشومسكي :</span></p><p dir="rtl" style="font-size:11pt;padding:0;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin:0;color:#000000;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-weight:bold">ما يخيف أمريكا في العالم العربي ليس الجماعات المتطرفة بل استقلال الشعوب وتحررها</span></p><p dir="rtl" style="font-size:11pt;padding:0;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin:0;color:#000000;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1155cc;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline"><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.google.com/url?q%3Dhttp://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q%253Dcache:http://www.chomsky.info/articles/20110204.htm%2526safe%253Dactive%2526strip%253D1%26amp;sa%3DD%26amp;ust%3D1455825042913000%26amp;usg%3DAFQjCNGlZdD8goZYkBtft_lbHTssQKCzsg&sa=D&ust=1455825042924000&usg=AFQjCNFu5ohJx_Nxf6CN3pBeaWtqhjzVgA" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:inherit">http://fb.me/2wiLOzMLU </a></span></p><p dir="rtl" style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;height:11pt;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-weight:bold"></span></p><p dir="rtl" style="font-size:11pt;padding:0;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin:0;color:#000000;text-align:justify"><span style="font-size: